documentation.text:
createPool creates pool which integrate with compound's staking
 startDate is date of starting pool, from this date pool's functions enable
 participationEndDate is date after which the play function is not available
 endDate is date of pool's end, enable to choose winner after this date
 participationAmount is required amount for participation
 isLottery if true it is a lottery pool, otherwise it is a savings pool

play spends user money to compound mint
 pool is address of pool

setWinner set pool's winner, redeem all assets from compound
 pool is address of pool

claim transfer asset from selt to user, winner also receive additional reward
 pool is address of pool
